    "description": {
      "value": "<p><a href=\"https://aonprd.com/RacesDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Samsaran\">Samsaran</a>&nbsp;only.</p>\n<p>Fighting in the mountains of Zi Ha has trained samsaran slayers to strike the unwary with deadly attacks from above. If a slayer deals sneak attack damage to a creature that is unaware of his presence while he is standing on higher ground than his target, he does not have to roll sneak attack damage; instead, the sneak attack deals maximum damage. The samsaran must be standing on solid ground to use this ability.</p>",
